{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/5_select.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Goblin Lands is a 2D strategy game in which you must conquer all the islands in each level to win. Select one or more of your islands and send your transports to overtake the enemy army, but be careful! The enemies will try to do the same with you, are you going to let other goblins become the masters of the seas?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/35_monster.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every 5 levels you will face a boss level, where obstacles in the form of monsters, storms or tornadoes will give you an added challenge. The difficulty of the game is incremental. Enemies will be faster, stronger and more determined. You will have to use the skill points you earn by defeating each boss to get upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/75_all.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will be able to obtain achievements, skins for the transports and discover all the content that the game offers. Will you be able to find the secret levels? And to obtain the achievements for the cheaters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 80 game levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 4 level maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 Hidden secret levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 20 game upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 +100 unlockable achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 24 island types of different styles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 8 types of transportation: 4 ships and 4 aircrafts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 10 unlockable skins for each transport</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 3 types of wandering transports</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 3 types of obstacles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 Original orchestral music</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3481450?t=1738518366","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738518366","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/010df62170b55106fb30229d1fa75721c4253c86/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738518366","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/010df62170b55106fb30229d1fa75721c4253c86/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738518366","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3487810,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/5_select.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Goblin Lands is a 2D strategy game in which you must conquer all the islands in each level to win. Select one or more of your islands and send your transports to overtake the enemy army, but be careful! The enemies will try to do the same with you, are you going to let other goblins become the masters of the seas?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/35_monster.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every 5 levels you will face a boss level, where obstacles in the form of monsters, storms or tornadoes will give you an added challenge. The difficulty of the game is incremental. Enemies will be faster, stronger and more determined. You will have to use the skill points you earn by defeating each boss to get upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/extras/75_all.gif?t=1738518366\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will be able to obtain achievements, skins for the transports and discover all the content that the game offers. Will you be able to find the secret levels? And to obtain the achievements for the cheaters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 80 game levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 4 level maps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 Hidden secret levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 20 game upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 +100 unlockable achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 24 island types of different styles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 8 types of transportation: 4 ships and 4 aircrafts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 10 unlockable skins for each transport</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 3 types of wandering transports</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 3 types of obstacles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2b50 Original orchestral music</p>","developers":["Hot Waffle Games"],"dlc":[3489280],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481450/header.jpg?t=1738518366","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"name":"Goblin Lands","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Dual Core<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Grap